and we define f of x to v,

25
00:01:34.435 --> 00:01:37.730
u of x times v of x,

26
00:01:37.730 --> 00:01:43.430
which is a Sine x times Cosine x then we're going to end up with this function.

27
00:01:43.430 --> 00:01:48.550
This function is Sine x times Cosine x.

28
00:01:48.550 --> 00:01:51.245
We see that this function is odd,

29
00:01:51.245 --> 00:01:55.400
