43
00:02:43.698 --> 00:02:51.280
We know that, the variance of x plus y is the variance

44
00:02:51.280 --> 00:03:00.010
of x plus the variance of y where x and y are random variables.

45
00:03:00.010 --> 00:03:03.420
Remember that variances are measured in squared units.

46
00:03:03.420 --> 00:03:08.325
This looks very much like the Pythagorean Theorem for right triangles,

47
00:03:08.325 --> 00:03:15.240
that one states that c squared equals a squared plus b squared.

