00:05:25.150 --> 00:05:29.301
definition the inner product between the two random variables,

75
00:05:29.301 --> 00:05:33.775
divided by the length of the first random variable,

76
00:05:33.775 --> 00:05:37.742
times the length of the second random variable.

77
00:05:37.742 --> 00:05:43.940
And if we now write this out using the definition of our inner product,

78
00:05:43.940 --> 00:05:50.087
